&lt;p&gt;We blame the mind like a monkey, it keeps dancing and makes the body and the world around dance and create problems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;See the beauty of mind, it can dance and without your notice, it can leap to a completely unrelated subject, location and time. Without this capability of mind no creativity is possible. No &amp;lsquo;hope&amp;rsquo; is possible. No temporary relief from present problems is possible.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
